column6: "A PLAGUE OF LOCUSTS" pt. 2 Johnny finds himself in the war-torn Balkans in a mysterious castle filled with dark secrets and deadly phantoms. It's the biggest fight of the Torch's life - because this time what he can't see... CAN kill him! [This is a resolicitation, all previous orders are cancelled.] 32 PGS./MARVEL PSR...$2.99
